🔹 Arduino Basics 

🧠 Learnings:
1. Types of Arduino boards (UNO, Mega)
2. Pin types: digital, analog, PWM, power
3. Sketch structure: setup() and loop()
4. Common functions: digitalWrite(), digitalRead(), analogRead(), analogWrite()

🛠️ Hands-on:
1. Blinking LED with digitalWrite
2. Reading a potentiometer with analogRead
